snippet.title: Therizinosaurus Gameplay | Showcase - Dinosaur King Arcade Game 恐竜キング
snippet.description:
Dinosaur King Showcase 18 - Therizinosaurus
ft. Dr. Spike Taylor VS Zoe

Therizinosaurus テリジノサウルス 鐮刀龍
Element : Secret 秘密
Strength : 2000
Name Meaning : Scythe Lizard
Length: 9-10 meters (30-33 feet)
[ http://dinosaurking.wikia.com/wiki/Therizinosaurus ]

VS

Pachycephalosaurus & Deinonychus

I gonna make a series of dinosaur showcase videos including moves and super moves for documentary of dinosaur king
